display_long_description:
Start your fantasy journey with this magical jigsaw puzzle game.
Professional 3D modeling, Soothing alpha brainwave music helps you relax your brain and improve attentionprecise, Wonderful movements allow you to immerse yourself in the game.

[media]
◈The game has 25, 50, 100, 600 and other challenging gameplay modes waiting for you to experience!

[media]
◈This edition contains a picture of the Mona Lisa, van gogh Starry Night，Qingming Map, lotus flowers, a pottery figurine from the Tang Dynasty, and a magnolia vase. 
[media]

◈We will update DLC periodically, please stay tuned.
[media] 

If you have any questions or suggestions, 
you can communicate here:

https://discord.gg/aqV9QaertN
